text: Two Arts Plaza will be an 18-story class-A office skyscraper located at Routh Street and Spur 366 (Woodall Rodgers Freeway) in the Arts District of Downtown Dallas, Texas (USA). ==See also== * One Arts Plaza == References == == External links == *Two Arts Plaza * One Arts Plaza * The Billingsley Company Category:Office buildings completed in 2007 Category:Skyscraper office buildings in Dallas
